    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後、衣装デザイナーの事務所",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん……\nこれが、コンテスト用に作った新しい衣装……",
      "startTime": 5.189687039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装なら……\n釣りをしてても、一目でアイドルだって分かる……",
      "startTime": 10.766667223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "これでアピールはばっちり……\nこの新衣装でオーディションを突破する……！",
      "startTime": 16.3027579945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "セーラーか……海で着るにはぴったりの衣装だな\n確かに、これなら目立てそうだが……",
      "startTime": 24.6666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、浮かない顔してる……\nこの衣装に不満があるの……？",
      "startTime": 32.3333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "不満というか……俺は釣りのことは詳しくないが……\nその格好で冬の海釣りって、寒くないのか？",
      "startTime": 39.6482752397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……！！\nそれは盲点だった……",
      "startTime": 45.166667223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、冬の海釣りは寒さとの戦い……\nこんな薄着じゃ、凍えて釣りどころじゃない……",
      "startTime": 51.7669181414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そこはもっと早く気付くべきだったな……",
      "startTime": 55.3333319029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうする？　この衣装は別の機会で着ることにして\n今回は他のアピール方法を考えるか？",
      "startTime": 63.0318683189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "それはダメ……アピールが下手な私には\nアイドル衣装が絶対必要……",
      "startTime": 69.2887675717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装じゃ寒さに耐えられないのなら……\n耐えられるように、対策すればいい……",
      "startTime": 75.4333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私に考えがある……\nオーディションまでに冬の寒さを攻略してみせる……！",
      "startTime": 80.9459321685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "startTime": 85.5000035446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "寒さを攻略すると息巻いていたが\n雫は何をする気なんだ？　無茶しないといいが……",
      "startTime": 90.8999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます",
      "startTime": 95.8333339376,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 95.8333339376
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、おはよう……\n雫？　どうして練習着なんだ？",
      "startTime": 100.7333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "コンテストに向けて、今日から毎日ランニングする……\nこれはそのための服装……",
      "startTime": 107.9654876316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今は真冬だぞ？\nそんな薄着で外を走ったら寒いだろ",
      "startTime": 112.0999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "それが狙い……この格好で外を走って寒さに慣れる……",
      "startTime": 115.0666672709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "真冬に薄着でも平気でいられれば……\nセーラーで海釣りだって出来るようになるはず……！",
      "startTime": 123.4333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "寒さを攻略するって\n気合いで我慢するって意味だったのか？",
      "startTime": 129.8999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "気合いは大事……心頭滅却すればなんとやら……\n気合いで寒さは克服出来る……",
      "startTime": 137.0999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "心頭滅却は熱さを我慢する時に言う言葉だからな？",
      "startTime": 139.6000006042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションまで時間がない……今はどんなことでも\nやれることは全部やっておきたい……",
      "startTime": 147.5999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "後で「もっと頑張っておけば良かった」って\n後悔したくないから……",
      "startTime": 153.7754523628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\n雫がそこまで言うなら止めないが、無理はするなよ",
      "startTime": 157.8999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……コンテストに出るためなら……\nどんな過酷なトレーニングも耐え抜いてみせる……！",
      "startTime": 165.6270401479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（熱意があるのはいいが、少し心配だな……）",
      "startTime": 169.4333339376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night"
    },
