    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、雫？　迎えに来たぞー\n……ん？　部屋がやけに寒いな",
      "startTime": 181.116681719,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3915.3134286000013,
          "startTime": 185.0319951476
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます……",
      "startTime": 185.4333329203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、おはよ……うわあああっ！\n雫！？　その格好は一体……",
      "startTime": 190.4094503939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "これも寒さ対策の一環……寒さに慣れるために\n普段から薄着で過ごすようにしてる……",
      "startTime": 197.8666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、真冬の海を再現するために……\n冷房を最大にして部屋の温度を限界まで下げてある……",
      "startTime": 204.9333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "寮のリビングで真冬の海を再現するんじゃない\nエアコンの温度を戻して、服もちゃんと着てくれ",
      "startTime": 213.3458401376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "む……分かった……。冷房を最大にするのは\n自分の部屋にいる時だけにする……",
      "startTime": 221.4123653324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "自分の部屋ならいいって訳でもないが……\n間違っても水着姿で宅配便を受け取りに出るなよ",
      "startTime": 227.9273158014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "startTime": 231.599999587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてバツが悪そうな顔をしているんだ？\nまさか……もうやらかした後なのか？",
      "startTime": 236.6000158151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……配達の人は女性だったから……",
      "startTime": 240.3333257994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "それは大丈夫とは言わないぞ",
      "startTime": 244.1666591328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening"
