      "text": "大丈夫か、顔色が良くないぞ\nレッスン中もふらついていたし……",
      "startTime": 254.9333384037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "心配ない……\nちょっと疲れてるだけ……",
      "startTime": 259.4000172774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "疲れているだけには見えないぞ\n念のため熱を測ってみよう",
      "startTime": 264.6333384037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk026.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい、平気……そろそろお仕事に行かないと……\n……あ……",
      "startTime": 272.5026733717,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
